cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about designing coordination algorithms for a simulated swarm, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (MAS) and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also discusses the performance of the swarm in various tasks, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The use of communication models and coordination algorithms implies that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
